# 🌍 Global CO2 Emissions Tracker by Sector

This project visualizes and analyzes global CO₂ emissions across countries and sectors. It includes a Tableau dashboard and a policy brief to identify top polluters and support climate policy decisions.

## 📊 Dashboard Features

- Interactive world map showing CO₂ emissions per capita 
- Filters by year, country
- Highlights of top 10 emitters (total and per capita)

## 🛠️ Data Preparation

Using Python (Pandas):

- Imported multi-year emissions data
- Calculated:Emissions_per_Capita 
- Cleaned and exported as `cleaned_emissions_per_capita.csv`

## 📄 Deliverables

- `emissions_dashboard.pbix`: Bi dashboard file


## 🧰 Tools Used

- Python (Pandas)
- power  bi
- Excel (for formatting brief)

## 📌 Objective

Help policymakers and researchers:
- Track emissions trends
- Compare countries by economic and demographic efficiency
- Identify sectoral priorities for emissions reduction
